1
00:00:01,710 --> 00:00:03,545
WHAT ARE THE ODDS?

2
00:00:03,545 --> 00:00:05,881
YOU AND I MEETING
LIKE THIS.

3
00:00:05,881 --> 00:00:08,383
YOU KNOW, BEING
A SENTIMENTAL VIRGO AND ALL,

4
00:00:08,383 --> 00:00:11,428
I CAN'T HELP FEELING WE WERE
DESTINED TO MEET.

5
00:00:11,428 --> 00:00:13,180
OR PERHAPS
I FOUND YOU BECAUSE

6
00:00:13,180 --> 00:00:15,599
YOU JUST STOPPED EMITTING
THOSE LIGHT PARTICLES.

7
00:00:15,599 --> 00:00:17,434
THAT'S PROBABLY IT!

8
00:00:17,434 --> 00:00:19,144
(Groans)

9
00:00:22,940 --> 00:00:25,317
HE FORCED ME BACK.
HOLD ON!

10
00:00:25,317 --> 00:00:28,695
GOOD LUCK HITTING ME WITH
THAT BIG BLADE OF YOURS!

11
00:00:28,695 --> 00:00:30,489
HE DODGED IT!

12
00:00:30,489 --> 00:00:32,950
BEFORE I LEAVE...

13
00:00:32,950 --> 00:00:35,118
I THINK I'LL COLLECT
A LITTLE SOUVENIR!

14
00:00:35,118 --> 00:00:38,038
DON'T YOU...TOUCH ME!

15
00:00:38,038 --> 00:00:39,623
(Grunts)

16
00:00:40,624 --> 00:00:42,626
(Shots firing)

17
00:00:49,633 --> 00:00:51,718
(Slash)

18
00:00:51,718 --> 00:00:53,303
HE HAS A BEAM SABER?

19
00:00:57,057 --> 00:00:59,059
(Groans)

