394
00:20:42,575 --> 00:20:44,368
MY NAME'S
SAJI CROSSROAD.

395
00:20:44,368 --> 00:20:46,162
I LIVE HERE WITH
MY BIG SISTER.

396
00:20:49,039 --> 00:20:51,876
SETSUNA F. SEIEI.

397
00:20:51,876 --> 00:20:55,546
SEIEI?
THAT'S AN UNUSUAL NAME.

398
00:20:55,546 --> 00:20:57,131
NICE TO MEET YOU.

